  "texts": [
    "We use the hyperparameters used by Meng et al. (2024), who conducted an extensive hyperparameter search.",
    "For our newly introduced hyperparameter, α, we search in the range {0.1, 0.25, 0.5}.",
    "Training data.",
    "We perform RLHF in an on-policy setting, where outputs are sampled from the policy being optimized.",
    "However, generating outputs during training is computationally expensive."
  ]
